,'dataLayer','GTM-TQCNMQ5S');</script>\r\n<!-- End Google Tag Manager -->\r\n\r\n</head>\r\n<body class=\"sustainability--detail en\">\r\n<input id=\"menu-toggle\" type=\"checkbox\" class=\"ipt-toggle\" tabindex=\"-1\">\r\n<input id=\"search-toggle\" type=\"checkbox\" class=\"ipt-toggle\" tabindex=\"-1\">\r\n<header id=\"site-header\" class=\"site-header\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<h1 class=\"site-id\"><a href=\"/en/index.html\" class=\"logo\" aria-label=\"Return to Home\">Nomura Research Institute (NRI)</a></h1>\r\n<nav class=\"nav-global\">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class=\"--service\"><a href=\"/en/service/index.html\">Services &amp; Solutions</a></li>\r\n<li class=\"--knowledge\"><a href=\"/en/knowledge/index.html\">Knowledge &amp; Insights</a></li>\r\n<li class=\"--company\"><a href=\"/en/company/index.html\">About NRI</a></li>\r\n<li class=\"--sustainability\"><a href=\"/en/sustainability/index.html\">Sustainability</a></li>\r\n<li class=\"--media\"><a href=\"/en/media/index.html\" target=\"ownedmedia\">&amp;N Future Creation Lab.</a></li>\r\n<li class=\"--search\"><label for=\"search-toggle\" class=\"btn-search\" tabindex=\"0\" id=\"search-toggle-btn\"><span class=\"sr-only\">Onsite Search</span></label></li>\r\n<li class=\"--menu\"><label for=\"menu-toggle\" class=\"btn-menu\" tabindex=\"0\" id=\"menu-toggle-btn\"><span>Menu</span></label></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</nav>\r\n<nav class=\"nav-support\">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a href=\"/en/news/index.html\">News</a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"//ir.nri.com/en/ir.html\">Investor Relations</a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"/en/feedback.html\">Contact Us</a></li>\r\n<li class=\"--lang\"><label for=\"language\" class=\"slt-lang\"><select id=\"language\" aria-label=\"Select display language\"><option value=\"jp\">日本語</option><option value=\"en\" selected=\"selected\">English</option><option value=\"cn\" lang=\"zh-CN\">中文简体</option></select></label></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</nav>\r\n</div>\r\n<nav class=\"nav-search\">\r\n<div class=\"container\" id=\"search-box\">\r\n<form action=\"/en/search/index.html\" method=\"get\">\r\n<fieldset class=\"fld-search\">\r\n<legend><span class=\"sr-only\">Keyword search: keyword</span></legend>\r\n<input type=\"search\" name=\"q\" value=\"\" placeholder=\"Keyword search: keyword\" class=\"ipt-search\" maxlength=\"100\"><button type=\"submit\" class=\"btn-search\">Search</button>\r\n<ul class=\"lst-suggested-keywords\"></ul>\r\n</fieldset>\r\n</form>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4>Popular search terms</h4>\r\n<ul class=\"lst-popularword\"></ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</nav>\r\n</header>\r\n<main>\r\n<header class=\"page-header\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<h1 class=\"ttl-page\">Message from the President</h1>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</header>\r\n<article class=\"page-content\">\r\n<div class=\"container --slim --migration\">\r\n\r\n<section>\r\n<div class=\"l-top_message\">\r\n\t<p class=\"text-alignCenter\"><img src=\"/content/900012178.jpeg\">\r\n\t</p>\r\n\t<p class=\"text-sizeMedium text-alignRight space-mt-20\">\r\n\t\tNomura Research Institute, Ltd.<br>\r\n\t\t<img src=\"/content/900012176.jpeg\" style=\"display: inline;\">\r\n\t</p>\r\n\t<p class=\"text-sizeMedium space-mt-10\" style=\"text-align: justify; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\">\r\n\t\tSince being established in 1965, Nomura Research Institute, Ltd. (NRI) has contributed to enriched lives of\r\n\t\tpeople through businesses such as consulting and IT solutions. The company&rsquo;s founding prospectus mentions\r\n\t\tthe will to &ldquo;promote industrial economy and serve society,&rdquo; and the spirit of creating new social\r\n\t\tvalue and solving social issues through our core business has been inherited to the present day as our DNA. This\r\n\t\tspirit is the foundation of the sustainability management of the NRI Group. We view creating sustainable society\r\n\t\tand realizing NRI Group's growth strategy are one and the same, and we will also grow through the creation of\r\n\t\tsocial value, with the aim of continuing to make the NRI Group indispensable for society.\r\n\t</p>\r\n\t<p class=\"text-sizeMedium space-mt-30\" style=\"text-align: justify; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\">\r\n\t\tSocial issues such as climate change have become more and more complicated in recent times, but digital\r\n\t\ttechnologies are sure to play a major role in their resolution. At NRI, we focus on innovation that utilizes\r\n\t\tdigital technologies (digital transformation, or &ldquo;DX&rdquo;) to create value in a wide range of fields,\r\n\t\tfrom the transformation of companies and businesses to the resolution of social issues. DX with a particular\r\n\t\tfocus on the resolution of social issues is called DX3.0. It involves the promotion of co-creation with\r\n\t\tstakeholders based on various themes for addressing social issues, such as carbon neutrality, regional\r\n\t\trevitalization/smart technologies, and the circular economy.\r\n\t</p>\r\n\t<p class=\"text-sizeMedium space-mt-30\" style=\"text-align: justify; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\">\r\n\t\tThe NRI Group will continue to build a better society by unlocking the full potential of each and every one of\r\n\t\tour diverse employees and increasing our organizational capability so that we can help contribute to achieving\r\n\t\tthe SDGs for common global issues. We will listen closely to the opinions of our diverse stakeholders over the\r\n\t\tworld and regulate our own behavior while striving to build sustainable futures together with you all.\r\n\t</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n</div>\r\n</article>\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<a href=\"/en/sustainability/index.html\" class=\"btn-primary\">Sustainability</a>\r\n</div>\r\n</main>\r\n<aside>\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<nav class=\"nav-imageindex\">\r\n<h2 class=\"ttl-lv2\">Sustainability</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class=\"--top\"><a href=\"/en/sustainability/index.html\">\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"/content/000000168.avif\" alt=\"\">\r\n<figcaption>\r\n<h3>Sustainability TOP</h3>\r\n</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n</a></li>\r\n<li class=\"--message\"><a href=\"/en/sustainability/top_message.html\">\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"/content/000000169.avif\" alt=\"\">\r\n<figcaption>\r\n<h3>Message from the President</h3>\r\n</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n</a></li>\r\n<li class=\"--management\"><a href=\"/en/sustainability/management/index.html\">\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"/content/000000170.avif\" alt=\"\">\r\n<figcaption>\r\n<h3>NRI Sustainability Management Policy</h3>\r\n</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n</a></li>\r\n<li class=\"--materiality\"><a href=\"/en/sustainability/materiality/index.html\">\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"/content/000000171.avif\" alt=\"\">\r\n<figcaption>\r\n<h3>Materiality Topics</h3>\r\n</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n</a></li>\r\n<li class=\"--library\"><a href=\"/en/sustainability/index.html#section-08\">\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"/content/000000172.avif\" alt=\"\">\r\n<figcaption>\r\n<h3>Library</h3>\r\n</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</nav>\r\n</div>\r\n</aside>\r\n<footer id=\"site-footer\" class=\"site-footer\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n    <nav class=\"nav-breadcrumbs\" aria-label=\"breadcrumb trail\">\r\n  <div class=\"container\">\r\n      <ul>\r\n      <li><a href=\"/en/index.html\">HOME</a></li>\r\n      <li><a href=\"/en/sustainability/index.html\">Sustainability</a></li>\r\n      <li>Message from the President</li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n    </div>\r\n    </nav>\r\n<h2 class=\"logo\"><span class=\"sr-only\">Nomura Research Institute (NRI)</span></h2>\r\n<nav class=\"nav-sitemap\">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class=\"--service\">\r\n<h3><a href=\"/en/service/index.html\">Services &amp; Solutions</a></h3>\r\n<div>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a href=\"/en/service/index.html#section-03\">Search by Industry</a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"/en/service/index.html#section-04\">Search by Theme</a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"/en/service/solution/index.html\">Service &amp; Solution List</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"--knowledg